wikipedia_page.main: Lyn Parker (born 25 November 1952) is a British civil servant, diplomat, and legal scholar. He was the British High Commissioner to Cyprus from 2001 to 2005, the British Ambassador to the Netherlands from 2005 to 2009, and Chef de Cabinet to the President of the International Criminal Court from 2011 to 2016.
